description: This Chainlink VRF top 1% rating Anurak purrs with a rating of 93, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 93, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 5 for East, Stringalong for South, and 8 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20931-75783-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
